{"tid":729099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持用廣東話字取代書面語","createTime":"2018-07-04T09:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T16:29:35.000Z","uid":144372,"like":50,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"01967f26b742eca20ad2681c00cbd0cb63145c46","tid":729099,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"書面語根本係以中國北方語言為基礎<br />\n你連登仔話同普通話唔同<br />\n只係因為中國喺1949之後多咗好多共產詞語<br />\n而書面語根本只係冇畀共產污染嘅北方語言<br />\n<br />\n100年前講我手寫我口<br />\n而家都仲有人反對<br />\n而而家香港政治形勢下<br />\n鼓吹廣東話字基本上係本土派唯一做到嘅嘢"},{"pid":"c64961d20b4c4b598ec93a0b4b2e1ce7ff8f80e4","tid":729099,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e69df97b362484a0aee89c3595c7105b704ef1b","tid":729099,"uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c64961d20b4c4b598ec93a0b4b2e1ce7ff8f80e4","tid":729099,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:24:14.000Z","msg":"冇共產污染嘅所謂書面語<br />\n一樣唔係香港人母語"},{"pid":"8eb19c692f8b9c443a75242dbb658dac5113b17b","tid":729099,"uid":163974,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"你支持有撚用"},{"pid":"0b526db026e9f29e7e5f34f12db3772ca15ab0de","tid":729099,"uid":144372,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8eb19c692f8b9c443a75242dbb658dac5113b17b","tid":729099,"uid":163974,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"你支持有撚用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"如果冇用咁你都唔使入嚟啦"},{"pid":"222983b503f1e09a2d774fbea50c88deced6f17d","tid":729099,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"我都想<br />\n不過要教左每個廣東話字點寫先"},{"pid":"c6602ccb29b128066167f6fd28985b9bf7611c04","tid